text: Susan Graham (born 20 August 1968) is a New Zealand taekwondo athlete. She competed at the 1988 Summer Olympics and 1992 Summer Olympics. Taekwondo was a demonstration sport at those Olympics. She competed in the heavyweight class. Graham won the silver medal in the 1992 competition. At the 1992 Asian Taekwondo Championships, she won the bronze medal in the heavyweight category. == References == Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Olympic silver medalists for New Zealand Category:Taekwondo practitioners
